  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Whether in your hand or draped around your body, the spiked chain serves as both weapon and shield.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Wis 15, Exotic Weapon Proficiency (spiked chain), Kyton Style, base attack bonus +5, Knowledge (planes) 3 ranks, ki pool class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When using Kyton Style, you gain a +1 shield bonus to your Armor Class as long as you are wielding a spiked chain. If the spiked chain is magical, add 1/2 its enhancement bonus to this shield bonus. If the spiked chain has the vicious ability, instead add its full enhancement bonus to the shield bonus.",
